column2: SELECT yg.specobjid, yg.z, yg.zErr, yg.fracDeV_r, yg.petroR5#_r, yg.petroR5#Err_r,     sigma_balmer, sigma_balmer_err, sigma_forbidden, sigma_forbidden_err,     gsl.h_alpha_eqw as HAEW, gsl.h_alpha_eqw_err as HAEWerr,     sqrt(gsl.oii_#_eqw*gsl.oii_#_eqw) as O2EW,     sqrt(gsl.oii_#_eqw_err*gsl.oii_#_eqw_err) as O2EWerr,     yg.objId, yg.photz, yg.photzerr, yg.absmagU, yg.absMagG, yg.absMagR, yg.absMagI, yg.absMagZ, yg.modelMagErr_r INTO MyDB.yourgalaxyparams FROM MyDB.yourgalaxies as yg JOIN galSpecLine as gsl on gsl.specObjID = yg.specObjID WHERE  gsl.oii_#_eqw between # and #
